{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\uc1\htmautsp\deff2{\fonttbl{\f0\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}{\f2\fcharset0 Segoe UI;}}{\colortbl\red0\green0\blue0;\red255\green255\blue255;}\loch\hich\dbch\pard\plain\ltrpar\itap0{\lang1033\fs18\f2\cf0 \cf0\ql{\f2 {\ltrch Zero Day Residual Provision (Member)}\li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
{\f2 {\ltrch The provision allows the employee whom is partially disabled to work on a trial basis immediately, while}\li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
{\f2 {\ltrch continuing to satisfy the elimination period. Total disability is never required}\li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
{\f2 {\ltrch Earnings threshold to be considered partially disabled is set at 80% of indexed monthly earnings during}\li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
{\f2 {\ltrch regular occupation period and 60% of indexed monthly earnings during gainful occupation period.}\li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
{\f2 {\ltrch This means any injury or sickness for which an employee, within the designated number of months before}\li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
{\f2 {\ltrch the effective date of coverage under the Group policy, incurred charges, received medical treatment,}\li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
{\f2 {\ltrch consultation, care, or services, including diagnostic measures, took prescribed drugs or medicines.}\li0\ri0\sa0\sb0\fi0\ql\par}
}
